document_data.name: Haniah Dales
document_data.mainbody:
'''Haniah Dales''' was a [[half-elf]] who arrived in the village of [[Hilltop]] in the [[Silver Marches]] in [[1372 DR]].

When [[kobold]]s attacked the village, she was forced to handle the aftermath of the attack because the mayor, [[Veraunt Shuttlescomb]], was beyond drunk.<ref>
